          Passion & reward

    section.slide: div
      h2 You might encounter...
      ul
        li Bugs or issues (tickets on trac)
          ul
            li Try (to learn)
              ,
              a href="http://trac.ckan.org/report"
                | search trac
            li CKAN issues moved
              ,
              i.icon.icon-hand-right
              ,
              a href="https://github.com/okfn/ckan/issues"
